===Etymology===
{{dercat|nl|odt|frk|gmw-pro|gem-pro|ine-pro|inh=4}}
From {{inh|nl|dum|sullen|solen, suelen, sollen, sullen}}, from {{inh|nl|odt|*sulan}}, from {{inh|nl|gmw-pro|*skulan}}, from {{inh|nl|gem-pro|*skulaną}}. Compare {{cog|de|sollen}}, {{cog|en|shall}}, {{cog|da|skulle}}.

