===Verb===
{{nl-verb}}

# {{lb|nl|auxiliary|present tense}} Used to form the [[future tense]] of a verb, together with an [[infinitive]]; [[will]], [[going to]]
#: {{ux|nl|Het '''zal''' toch niet werken.|It '''will''' not work anyway.}}
#: {{ux|nl|Dat '''zal''' niet gebeuren.|That '''will''' not happen.}}
# {{lb|nl|auxiliary|past tense}} Used to form the [[conditional mood]] of a verb, together with an infinitive; [[would]]
#: {{ux|nl|Het werk '''zou''' nu af zijn geweest als jij je niet had verslapen.|The work '''would''' have been finished now if you hadn't overslept.}}
#: {{ux|nl|Dat '''zou''' ik niet doen als ik jou was.|I '''would''' not do that if I were you.}}
# {{lb|nl|modal auxiliary}} Used to indicate [[intent]] or [[disposition]] to perform an action in the [[future]]: [[will]], [[shall]], be [[going to]], [[may]], [[might]]
#: {{ux|nl|Het '''zou''' vandaag regenen.|It '''was going to''' rain today.}}
#: {{ux|nl|'''Zal''' ik eerst gaan?|'''Shall''' I go first?}}

